{"tid":2256424,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"12港人送中︱世界各地均有聲援行動 羅冠聰預告在倫敦集會發言","createTime":"2020-10-24T10:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T14:26:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8568e1ab35613a383d1dd23de6f725d4eeef3835","tid":2256424,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:50:41.000Z","msg":"12 名港人被秘密關押於深圳鹽田看守所至63日，12港人關注組發起「國際連動 聲援十二港人」行動，世界各地都有支持者響應。在英國倫敦，「Fight for Freedom, Stand with Hong Kong」將在英國時間周六下午2時、即本港時間今晚 9 時舉行集會聲援 12 人（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk/posts/1073497169747617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandwithhk%2Fposts%2F1073497169747617&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=cdfadca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk/posts/1073497169747617</a>），流亡海外的前香港眾志主席羅冠聰、Hong Kong Watch發起人羅傑斯（Benedict Rogers）將會現身發言。另外，美國、瑞典、韓國和日本都分別有聲援行動。<br />\n<br />\n羅傑斯昨晚（23日）在Twitter (<a href=\"https://twitter.com/benedictrogers/status/1319931463056445441/photo/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbenedictrogers%2Fstatus%2F1319931463056445441%2Fphoto%2F1&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=0a1b067b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbenedictrogers%2Fstatus%2F1319931463056445441%2Fphoto%2F1&h=5cd5c202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/benedictrogers/status/1319931463056445441/photo/1</a>) 上載一段，「毋忘義士、釋放十二」的手寫中文字，呼籲世界關注12港青被關押的問題，他同時表明將會與羅冠聰一同在今日的倫敦塔橋（Tower Bridge）集會中發言，聲援12港人。今次亦是羅冠聰流亡後首次公開演說。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201024/ZN4IQQSAVVDDDKV7USAGIKZC5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201024%2FZN4IQQSAVVDDDKV7USAGIKZC5Q%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=b182e9e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201024%2FZN4IQQSAVVDDDKV7USAGIKZC5Q%2F&h=b3899a87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201024/ZN4IQQSAVVDDDKV7USAGIKZC5Q/</a>"},{"pid":"76355773c80ff48f401455fa077024d42dbb9f81","tid":2256424,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a141e672f6d62937efbeff8f1531ea2cfd53b64","tid":2256424,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf64d42f87adfe1698c58a58383e34a159cf618","tid":2256424,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdab42e5e941c518aab585ece79eeae4e5405e78","tid":2256424,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:52:01.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"5687dcc1f59ebba0a476621521289aa33f471e6a","tid":2256424,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76355773c80ff48f401455fa077024d42dbb9f81","tid":2256424,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\"